title: Motorcraft Auto Parts Supplier Celebrates 50 Years of Quality With Series of Special Events, Celebrations
description: Motorcraft® auto parts supplier is celebrating its 50th anniversary with a series of special events that highlight its heritage, including visitor giveaways at the Woodward Dream Cruise, a special Ford podcast presentation, and a showcase of its race car paint schemes in coordination with the National Hot Rod Association and NASCAR events over Labor Day weekend.
